parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the theme that you're deleting.

parameters.name: ThemeId
parameters.description: An ID for the theme that you want to delete.

parameters.name: VersionNumber
parameters.description: The version of the theme that you want to delete. Note: If you don't provide a version number, you're using this call to DeleteTheme to delete all versions of the theme.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
